{"tid":855941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國慶升旗】新北萬人升旗好壯觀　國旗女孩長腿吸精","createTime":"2018-10-10T10:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T10:59:46.000Z","uid":72009,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4a892a6cd2522b7ff9709ce5e5c7061b7f6fb373","tid":855941,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"新北市107年國慶升旗典禮今天上午8時於板橋市民廣場舉行，雖然天公不做美變得濕冷，仍擋不住上萬名民眾熱情，共同到場搖旗歡慶雙十，除了市府身穿短褲背心的國旗女孩青春洋溢吸睛外，也有不少人一身國旗裝扮、紋身貼紙來參加，市長朱立倫率市府團隊及與會貴賓高唱國歌、國旗歌，連前副市長、國民黨新北市長參選人侯友宜來到台下默契與會，現場免費發送的 1010份「國旗桿不鏽鋼吸管」更是10分鐘全送完，幸運拿到民眾直說意義非凡；「好開心！」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181010/640_3138f5056bf05568b05aac74ddec8dad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181010%2F640_3138f5056bf05568b05aac74ddec8dad.jpg&h=06191d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有Ｄ不錯，除剩國旗背心..."},{"pid":"9bc1827793d52b6abd5710a9d8f7cfc60f59eaf1","tid":855941,"uid":197196,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"點解台妹個個都咁撚7正 反觀港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1625424ad810828df2af971b34d229fedf276f05","tid":855941,"uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/183547_6c72921845f423ca3d81ac901b7e0f46.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F183547_6c72921845f423ca3d81ac901b7e0f46.gif&h=54e34d82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9bd001c179462e73b0cfc95f27727307b977c0e","tid":855941,"uid":215864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"我可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b2ce651db437ca6b54b546f708709994abc1db","tid":855941,"uid":84212